<lb ed="I" n="0132b04"/>邑正郭祖願
<lb ed="I" n="0132b05"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0132b06"/>邑主呂伏歡
<lb ed="I" n="0132b07"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0132b08"/>像主<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">昭</unclear>道慶
<lb ed="I" n="0132b09"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0132b10"/>化主郭和悅
<lb ed="I" n="0132b11"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0132b12"/>邑子魏
<lb ed="I" n="0132b13"/></p></cb:div></cb:div><cb:div>
